text: Swan (Bulgarian: "Ле́бед", translit.: "Lébed") is a 1976 Bulgarian drama movie directed by Rumen Surdzhiyski and Georgi Kaloyanchev, Yordan Spirov, Mario Marinov, Yavor Milushev. ==Other websites== * Category:1976 drama movies Category:Bulgarian movies Category:Movies directed by Rumen Surdzhiyski
title: Swan (1976 movie)
